No. 241,

Misc.

Nevada Tax Commission v. Thompson, U. S. District Judge, et al. Harvey Dickerson, Attorney General of Nevada, for petitioner. Solicitor General Marshall, Assistant Attorney General Rogovin and Harold C. Wilkenjeld for respondent Thompson et al.

C. A. 9th Cir. and D. C. Nev. Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
